org.osate.xtext.aadl2.errormodel.errorModel

Interface ErrorPropagation

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AObject, Element, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, EventOrPropagation, org.eclipse.core.runtime.IAdaptable, NamedElement, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ErrorPropagationImpl

    public interface ErrorPropagation
extends NamedElement, EventOrPropagation
    A representation of the model object 'Error Propagation'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Observable
    • Kind
    • Feature
    • Not
    • Direction
    • Type Set

    See Also:
    ErrorModelPackage.getErrorPropagation()
